  "code": "union Shape is\n    CIRCLE(radius: double);\n    SQUARE(side: double);\nsi\narea(s: Shape) -> double is\n    if let c: CIRCLE = s then\n        return 3.14159d * c.radius * c.radius;\n    elif let q: SQUARE = s then\n        return q.side * q.side;\n    fi\n\n    return 0.0d;\nsi",
